title: You're Not Sorry (Taylor's Version)
description:
What is Taylor Swift really saying in You're Not Sorry? We have theories that this song could have some foreshadowing into the darker version of Taylor that was to come many years later. Plus, the career changing moment that happened that she swore she would tell her family for many years to come.
What do you think? Did we miss anything? Let us know it all, and whatever else is on your mind!
